# calendar_api
Google Calendar Event Search

### Installation ###

    pip install cal_event_search

## Prerequisites
    python >= 3.7
    qt>=5.9.7
    qtpy>=1.5.2
    google-api-python-client>=1.7.8
    google-auth>=1.6.3
    google-auth-httplib2>=0.0.3
    google-auth-oauthlib>=0.3.0
    google-pasta>=0.1.4
